^B@2^*BMB: ^*N|cp||at|Keep in mind that when you are missing four cards in a suit, the suit will divide 2-2 less than 41% of the time. Therefore, what you would like to do is ask your partner, "Do you have the @SQ or extra trump length (at least five)?" Even if partner has five low spades, your chances of not having a spade loser when missing three cards in the suit are excellent.|
