NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BMB: ^*N|cp||at|To find out, you bid 5@D. This is referred to as the "queen ask." Why 5@D? Because it is the cheapest artificial bid. Obviously, if diamonds are trumps, 5@D would be natural and non-forcing.|mb|5d|AN|queen ask|
