NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BMB: ^*N|cp||at|5@S denies the @SQ or extra length.
6@S shows the @SQ or extra length, and denies a side-suit king. If partner has the @SQ or extra length, he will control-bid his cheapest side-suit king:
5@H shows the @SQ or extra length and the @HK. It does not deny the @CK or @DK.
6@C shows the @SQ (or extra length) and the @CK. It denies the @HK. It does not deny the @DK.
6@D shows the @SQ (or extra length) and the @DK. It denies any other kings.|
